reviewText: This is the second copy that I bought of this movie, the first  was in a three-pack, but the second one was in a single movie format, and they both were the edited and censored version of the dvd. I feel ripped off because I paid for an uncensored movie and both screwed both times, a real waste of money on my part. watch out and to noboby, thank you.

Don't waste your money and time with this one. The point of a "sex comedy" is for it to be "sexy" and have "comedy," both of which have been cut and censored; the movie barely clocks in at approximately 65 minutes. The dvd is a bootleg off a television broadcast.
